# Demo: top negative log patterns
Output assets/edx-patterns.gif
Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 15
Set Width 1200
Set Height 300
Set Padding 12
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 25ms

Type "edx patterns list --negative --limit 5 --output table --columns count,delta,sentiment,pattern"
Sleep 600ms
Enter
Sleep 4.5s
